{"tid":838832,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"監犯為見托迪自願加監","createTime":"2018-09-27T12:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T13:07:09.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24d5fe1ad3800a5b1d15cb82f3c590f416abb470","tid":838832,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=0SoPDjFcrTt7RNAzShIFETOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3da11cbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】球星們不時都會探訪學校、醫院，以回饋社區，羅馬名宿托迪最近就分享一次探訪監獄的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n去年退役的傳奇前鋒托迪（Francesco Totti）最近推出自傳《Un Capitano》，在書中回憶起當年為羅馬探訪監獄：「我們參觀了那裡的監倉，那些監犯都非常高興，看到球員就像看到教宗一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n41歲的托迪指，當時有一名監犯一邊大叫一邊向前推，希望可以跟球員合照，只是沒有人讓他通過，「我真的不知道為甚麼他這樣有決心。」<br />\n<br />\n這名監犯可不是最瘋狂的，更有監犯本身在那次探訪前出獄，卻自願申請被監禁久一點，為的就是跟球員見面。他向獄方寫信表示：「就算我活多100年，都沒可能有這個機會跟托迪合照！」"},{"pid":"afd47a406485d53f77758679d6f629132e22f4bc","tid":838832,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"n賓為見豬蛇梁天奇自願入獄"},{"pid":"5dfe5f2c184fb8b73f9fc109880891ca5cec5582","tid":838832,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afd47a406485d53f77758679d6f629132e22f4bc","tid":838832,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"n賓為見豬蛇梁天奇自願入獄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"著撚左草啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5362207cb5d79d638ff8e02b4cd8909fbed682b","tid":838832,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dfe5f2c184fb8b73f9fc109880891ca5cec5582","tid":838832,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afd47a406485d53f77758679d6f629132e22f4bc","tid":838832,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"n賓為見豬蛇梁天奇自願入獄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"著撚左草啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"宜家連紐西蘭都有針"}]}